{{distinguish|Sanga language (Nigeria)}} {{Infobox language |name=Sanga |nativename=''Kisanga'' |states=[[Democratic Republic of Congo]] |region= |ethnicity=[[Sanga people]] |speakers={{sigfig|431,000|2}} |date=1991 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo languages|Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Benue–Congo languages|Benue–Congo]] |fam4=[[Bantoid languages|Bantoid]] |fam5=[[Bantu languages|Bantu]] |fam6=[[Luban languages|Luban]] |fam7=[[Luba languages]] |fam8=Kiluba |iso3=sng |glotto=sang1331 |glottorefname=Sanga (Democratic Republic of Congo) |guthrie=L.35 }}
